# ===================== MDK-ARM Keil 编译产物 =====================
# 匹配任意子目录下的 MDK-ARM 文件夹（APP/MDK-ARM、OTA/MDK-ARM 等）
**/MDK-ARM/**/Debug/
**/MDK-ARM/**/Release/
**/MDK-ARM/**/*.axf
**/MDK-ARM/**/*.hex
**/MDK-ARM/**/*.bin
**/MDK-ARM/**/*.map
**/MDK-ARM/**/*.lnp
**/MDK-ARM/**/*.htm
**/MDK-ARM/**/*.crf
**/MDK-ARM/**/*.d
**/MDK-ARM/**/*.o
**/MDK-ARM/**/*.dep
**/MDK-ARM/**/*.build_log.htm
**/MDK-ARM/**/*.bak
**/MDK-ARM/**/*.sctx
**/MDK-ARM/**/.#L.*

# Keil 工程用户配置（窗口布局、个人设置，每人本地不同）
*.uvgui*
*.uvguix.*
*.uvoptx
*.opt
*.bak
*.$$$
*.sav

# Keil RTE 运行时环境自动生成文件
**/MDK-ARM/RTE/
**/MDK-ARM/DebugConfig/
**/MDK-ARM/firmware/

# ===================== 全局编译/调试中间文件 =====================
*.elf
*.out
*.mem
*.log
*.trace
*.svd
*.i
*.ii
*.d
*.crf
*.o
*.obj
*.axf
*.elf
*.hex
*.bin
*.map

# ===================== 系统临时文件 =====================
# Windows
Thumbs.db
Desktop.ini
desktop.ini
*.tmp
*.temp
*.swp
*.swo

# macOS
.DS_Store
.AppleDouble
.LSOverride

# ===================== 仿真器/下载器缓存 =====================
JLinkLog.txt
JLinkSettings.ini
ST-LINK*.log
*.jlink
*.stld

# ===================== OTA/升级工具临时文件 =====================
upgrade_temp/
fw_temp/
*.ota
*.pack

# 压缩包（通常是编译输出或分发文件，不需要入库）
*.zip
*.rar
*.7z

# ===================== 编辑器/IDE 缓存 =====================
# VS Code
.vscode/
*.code-workspace

# CLion / IAR
.idea/
cmake-build-*/
*.ewd
*.ewp
*.eww

# ===================== 文档导出文件（按需保留） =====================
